From: Hiroki Negishi <hiroki.negishi.bx@bp.renesas.com>
Date: Thu, 30 Jun 2016 13:30:35 +0900
Subject: [PATCH 1515/2066] arm64: dts: r8a7795: Add MFIS Lock device node

Add MFIS Lock device node for R-Car Gen3 Hardware Spinlock driver.

Signed-off-by: Hiroki Negishi <hiroki.negishi.bx@bp.renesas.com>
Signed-off-by: Takeshi Kihara <takeshi.kihara.df@renesas.com>
[zou:Original patch taken from
git://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/linux/kernel/git/horms/renesas-bsp.git
 v4.9/rcar-3.5.1]
Signed-off-by: zou cao <cao.zou@windriver.com>
---
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/renesas/r8a7795.dtsi |    9 +++++++++
 1 files changed, 9 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/renesas/r8a7795.dtsi b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/renesas/r8a7795.dtsi
index 1bfa0a2..6b2b990 100644
--- a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/renesas/r8a7795.dtsi
+++ b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/renesas/r8a7795.dtsi
@@ -809,6 +809,15 @@
 			status = "okay";
 		};
 
+		mfis_lock: mfis-lock {
+			compatible =    "renesas,mfis-lock-r8a7795",
+					"renesas,mfis-lock";
+			reg = <0 0xe62600c0 0 0x0020>;
+			clocks = <&cpg CPG_MOD 213>;
+			power-domains = <&sysc R8A7795_PD_ALWAYS_ON>;
+			status = "okay";
+		};
+
 		pfc: pfc@e6060000 {
 			compatible = "renesas,pfc-r8a7795";
 			reg = <0 0xe6060000 0 0x50c>;
